l/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/punc/punc-12146/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/punc/punc-12146/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/punc/punc-12146/canvas/1/15eb85b5-5a91-4211-956d-7e57648de7f9","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2025-08-27T20:24:19.471Z","creator":"Olivia Flores","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>The figures on this lamp recall Barry (wearing blue) and Lena (wearing white in Hawaii). They are positioned as if charging toward the Mattress Man, hinting toward the confrontation that is about to take place.</p>"}],"target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/punc/punc-12146/canvas/1#xywh=10,454,438,488"},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/punc/punc-12146/canvas/1/b50590e9-f388-4018-95af-1a9d84a8940e","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2025-08-27T20:24:31.240Z","creator":"Olivia Flores","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Although the Mattress Man presents himself as a masculine, virile, strong man, in these scenes close to the end of the film, we see his inner weaknesses. First, he can’t stop saying “ow” as Georgia combs his hair. Next, he will back down when Barry confronts him.</p>"}],"target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/punc/punc-12146/canvas/1#xywh=718,533,306,306"}]}]}]}